OL,3,CFour years after ITV News exposed:
OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FThe whitewashed walls had turned
OL,7,Fblack, a furry fungus growing on every
OL,8,Fsurface. Water cascaded through light
OL,9,Ffittings and into plug sockets,
OL,10,Fplunging the properties into darkness.
OL,11,FThe floors were sodden.
OL,13,FTenants were forced to place buckets
OL,14,Fand baby baths under the leaking
OL,15,Fwater. The homes were infested with
OL,16,Fslugs and a environmental health
OL,17,Finspection found a mum and her two
OL,18,Fchildren were at risk of electrocution.
