OL,3,CFour years after ITV News exposed:
OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FOnly now, more than four year on, has
OL,7,Fthe Regulator withdrawn its regulatory
OL,8,Fnotice and removed the council from
OL,9,Fspecial measures, assessing the
OL,10,Fhousing service to be at acceptable
OL,11,Fand safe standards.
OL,13,FJason Perry, Executive Mayor of
OL,14,FCroydon, said: "This is a crucial
OL,15,Fmoment in the ongoing transformation
OL,16,Fof housing services in Croydon. We are
OL,17,Fcreating a borough that listens to
OL,18,Fresidents and invests in safer, better-
OL,19,Fquality homes. The work continues, and
OL,20,Fwe remain focused on delivering
OL,21,Fimprovements that benefit everyone."
