OL,3,CFour years after ITV News exposed:
OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FSusmita Sen, Director of Housing at
OL,7,FCroydon Council, said: "Lifting the
OL,8,Fregulatory notice marks an important
OL,9,Fstep in our ongoing efforts to improve
OL,10,Fhousing services. Whilst we've made
OL,11,Fimprovements, there is still work to
OL,12,Fbe done to meet residents'
OL,13,Fexpectations and continue enhancing
OL,14,Fservice quality."
OL,16,FFollowing a vote by residents, the
OL,17,FRegina Road estate exposed in the ITV
OL,18,FNews investigation are to be
OL,19,Fdemolished and replaced with a new
OL,20,F#100 million social housing
OL,21,Fdevelopment.
